data.description: NEW BEAUTIFUL CUSTOM 'CERTIFIED GREEN' POOL HOME - BUILT in 2022 and ONLY used as a seasonal residence!  Located in Central Florida's Premiere Active Adult Community ~ beautiful LAKE ASHTON!    This gorgeous custom St. Marks floorplan features 3 bedrooms /2 baths, split plan with additional Den/Office, beautifully centrally located large kitchen, large master ensuite, oversized roofed & screened veranda with gorgeous, large salt water heated pool, situated near 6th green of Lake Ashton's West golf course. This home has it all!  Graced with large 20" neutral toned ceramic tile extending from the foyer, through the living room, formal dining, kitchen, dinette, and continuing into the oversized flex space & laundry room and all baths. High volume ceilings are featured throughout, a custom coffered ceiling was added- perfectly positioned framing the wonderful open living room. Large triple sliding glass doors located across the back of the living room as well as additional large double sliding glass door located adjacent in the eat-in kitchen offers fabulous natural lighting throughout this home creating a bright, open atmosphere.  All the tall sliding glass doors open onto a fabulous, large roofed and screened veranda! Along with an extremely inviting 10 x 16 salt water heated pool~ perfect outdoor paradise you will enjoy year-round!  The addition of 1/2 wall plumbed with electric for the opportunity to add an outdoor summer kitchen if you so choose! Whether you are entertaining family & friends or simply relaxing while floating your days or evenings away in the privacy of your own pool ....  the fabulous view overlooking the golf course and the evenings you will be mesmerized by the most talked about, breathtaking sunsets you will ever see! This is a setting you will enjoy!      The centerpiece of this home features a wonderful, large inviting kitchen.  The spacious kitchen is a chef's dream! Excelling in an abundance counter space, beautiful 42" soft white glazed cabinets, customized large bank of drawers featuring tremendous storage, recessed lighting, stainless steel appliances and so much more!  The kitchen focal point of the kitchen is a wonderfully large counter-level granite island, stretching the entire length of the kitchen! This fully functional kitchen island offers gracious countertop space, large undermount sink, beautiful cabinetry, along with additional seating with ease. This is a kitchen you will enjoy for years to come!   The large master suite is situated opposite side of the home separate from the guest bedrooms and den. Offering you the utmost in privacy.  The master suite boosts (2) large walk-in closets, his and hers raised vanities, private water closet, beautiful tiled walk-in shower as well as a large soaking tub.   Offset from the eat-in kitchen features your Den/office.  Custom pocket doors allowing you the rare opportunity to close off this space for privacy and/or a bit of quiet time.   Additionally, this floor plan offers (2) nice size guest bedrooms -customizing bedroom #2 making it 2 feet bigger.  A wonderful guest bath featuring a fully tiled shower/bath along with raised vanity is conveniently located between the two bedrooms making this very accessible for your visiting guests.  This home is a MUST TO SEE!  NEW ST. MARKS home just built in 2022!!   CERTIFIED GREEN POOL HOME, featuring FABULOUS CUSTOM APPOINTMENTS located in BEAUTIFUL LAKE ASHTON!  Call today to schedule your appointment!
